        %h3 Find out what’s stealing your sleep.
        %img.left{:src=>"images/learn-steal.gif"}
        %p Understand and minimize the factors that negatively affect sleep, so you can take control of your nights. Use the visual analytical tools in your personal myZeo.com account to see trends and cause & effect patterns. 
        .clear
